NK034(ngi)001:0: rdzogs pa chen po gsang ba snying thig gi man
NK034(ngi)001:1: ngag zab pa po ti bzhi'i kha byang nyi mas
NK034(ngi)001:2: brgyan pa bzhugs so bcom ldan 'das rdo rje 'chang
NK034(ngi)001:3: chen po la phyag 'tshal lo 'jig rten gsum po
NK034(ngi)001:4: snang bar byed pa'i 'od ldan pa'i sangs rgyas rnams
NK034(ngi)001:5: kyi bde chen thugs la mnga' gnyis med rdo rje
NK034(ngi)001:6: lta bu'i ye shes can gzhan gyi rnam par rtog
NK034(ngi)001:7: pa'i zhen pa gcod la mkhas snang ba gnyis po
NK034(ngi)001:8: dag ni zad par mdzad la mkhas skye med snying
NK034(ngi)001:9: po rang rig dngos la spyod brgyud pa gsum gyi
NK034(ngi)001:10: rtsa ba nyid 'chang ba dam pa dus gsum bzhugs
NK034(ngi)001:11: pa'i sku gsum la gnyis med dad pa brtan pos
NK034(ngi)001:12: sems g.yos te lus ngag yid gsum gus pas phyag
NK034(ngi)001:13: 'tshal nas gsang ba'i yang bcud rnams ni gsal bya'i
NK034(ngi)001:14: phyir mos gus skal ldan rnams kyi don ched du
NK034(ngi)001:15: thugs rje chen po mchog la gsol btab nas yang
NK034(ngi)001:16: gsang sbas pa'i man ngag snying thig ma kha byang
NK034(ngi)001:17: rnam pa brgyad du ma bkod pa'i yang gab sbas
NK034(ngi)001:18: pa gsang ba snying gi nor lhag chad 'gyur ba
NK034(ngi)001:19: med pa'i don ched du gsang ba mchog gi yi
NK034(ngi)001:20: ge 'di dag ni ma 'ongs skal ldan rnams kyi
NK034(ngi)001:21: don ched du tshig don gsal bar 'di nyid 'bri
NK034(ngi)001:22: bar bya gsang ba gsang mchog bla na med pa'i
NK034(ngi)001:23: sde snying po yang nges gsang ba'i man ngag rnams
NK034(ngi)001:24: ras chod gzu lum nyid dang bral bya'i phyir 'gyur
NK034(ngi)001:25: med don gyi yi ge 'di ltar 'bri e ma
NK034(ngi)001:26: gsang mchog dam pa gzhan du ma bstan pa'o snying
NK034(ngi)001:27: las lhag pa'i man ngag snying thig la kha byang
NK034(ngi)001:28: rnams su bkod par ma phod pa'i rtsa rnams mdud
NK034(ngi)001:29: pa snying la 'dus pa ltar brgya dang bcu dgu
NK034(ngi)001:30: man ngag dam pa rnams yang gsang snying dang 'dra
NK034(ngi)001:31: ba bzhi la 'dus de kun mtshan tsam brjod par
NK034(ngi)001:32: mi phod pa'i bdag gi khong snying phyungs pa 'di
NK034(ngi)001:33: lta ste don gnyis rdzogs par 'dod pa'i skal ldan
NK034(ngi)001:34: gyis gsang ba dung yig can la goms par bya
NK034(ngi)001:35: de yi mtshan tsam brjod pa bla ma dang bde
NK034(ngi)001:36: gshegs mkha' 'gro rnams la bzod par gsol skal ldan
NK034(ngi)001:37: snying gi bu la dgos srid na 'di nyid tshig
NK034(ngi)001:38: tu brjod pa ma gtogs pa su yis thos na
NK034(ngi)001:39: mkha' 'gro'i chad pa phob de bas snying po sems
NK034(ngi)001:40: la rgyas thob la snying po byang chub bar du
NK034(ngi)001:41: khar mi dbyung gzhan gyis thos shing mthong na rang
NK034(ngi)001:42: srog tshig de bas rlung phyogs tsam du bsgrag pa
NK034(ngi)001:43: min 'byung ba'i sgra dang bral ba'i gnas su bskyal
NK034(ngi)001:44: skabs su blta zhing bsnyen bkur chen po bya rang
NK034(ngi)001:45: gis goms par byas la gter du sba gzhan du
NK034(ngi)001:46: bstan zhing gzhan la ma yin no yang gsang snying
NK034(ngi)001:47: dang 'dra ba'i man ngag la bstan pa thams cad
NK034(ngi)001:48: 'dus pa'i bu gcig po sus kyang byas pa med
NK034(ngi)001:49: pa'i yi ge nyid rang byung kun gyi thog mar
NK034(ngi)001:50: byung bas na skad dang brda rnams mi mthun med
NK034(ngi)001:51: pa'i phyir skal ldan rnams kyis mthong zhing bltas pa'i
NK034(ngi)001:52: tshe yi ge rang rang mthun pa nyid du shes
NK034(ngi)001:53: de yi dbang gis 'byung ba'i sgra dang bral sa
NK034(ngi)001:54: yis bsub cing chu yis khyer ba dang rlung gis
NK034(ngi)001:55: 'thor ba med cing mes bsregs bral skyes bu rnams
NK034(ngi)001:56: kyis 'jigs shing mthong ba med 'di ni bstan pa
NK034(ngi)001:57: thams cad 'dus pa'i gnad skal ldan snying gi bu
NK034(ngi)001:58: yis 'di bris te bstan pa gang la bab pa'i
NK034(ngi)001:59: kha dog ni rin chen snying po dag gis bris
NK034(ngi)001:60: nas ni rang gi lus dang 'bral ba med par
NK034(ngi)001:61: bcang lta zhing klog pa'i tshe na gzhan dag gis
NK034(ngi)001:62: 'di nyid mthong bar gyur na dngos grub yal de
NK034(ngi)001:63: phyir dur khrod dam ni nags kyi klong sus kyang
NK034(ngi)001:64: rgyu bar dka' ba'i gnas su ni chu gling la
NK034(ngi)001:65: sogs dben par bklag cing mchod 'di nyid su la
NK034(ngi)001:66: snang ba'i mi de ni skal dang ldan pa nges
NK034(ngi)001:67: par grol ba'o de ltar nges pa'i man ngag snying
NK034(ngi)001:68: gi nor rab tu zab la med thabs med pa
NK034(ngi)001:69: yi bdud rtsi'i thigs pa 'gro rnams nad sel ba'i
NK034(ngi)001:70: snying thig man ngag nges pa 'di dag gsang su
NK034(ngi)001:71: la'ang mi bstan rang gis sems la brnags snying po'i
NK034(ngi)001:72: don rnams lta zhing spyod pa las rlung dang ser
NK034(ngi)001:73: bu'i sgra tsam phyogs su spang gzhan rnams 'di dang
NK034(ngi)001:74: skal ba med pa'i mis mthong bar gyur yang dam
NK034(ngi)001:75: tshig chad par 'gyur thos par gyur na lus ngag
NK034(ngi)001:76: me yis bsreg de las rang gi sems la rgyas
NK034(ngi)001:77: btab ste rkun po'i nor ltar gsang zhing spyad par
NK034(ngi)001:78: bya su la'ang bsgrags pa med pa'i gsang ba 'di
NK034(ngi)001:79: skal ldan snying gi bu dang 'phrad par shog +thii
NK034(ngi)001:80: mchog tu gsang ba'i man ngag snying nor 'di mtshan
NK034(ngi)001:81: tsam brjod par bdag gis mi phod ste bla ma
NK034(ngi)001:82: brgyud pa rnams la gsol btab nas snyigs ma'i dus
NK034(ngi)001:83: su 'di nyid dgos srid pas snying thig zab pa'i
NK034(ngi)001:84: kha byang 'di nyid 'bri gsang chen snying dang 'dra
NK034(ngi)001:85: ba'i man ngag nyid yang dag rdzogs pa'i rdo rje
NK034(ngi)001:86: 'chang chen gyis sngon chad thugs kyi klong nas ma
NK034(ngi)001:87: rdol ba'i 'khor ba'i chos nyid gtan nas spang ba'i
NK034(ngi)001:88: phyir 'da' ba med las 'da' ba'i tshul bstan pa'i
NK034(ngi)001:89: ston pa mya ngan 'das pa'i rjes zhabs la nam
NK034(ngi)001:90: mkha' mi phyed bar snang nyid las kyang byin brlabs
NK034(ngi)001:91: thog mar rang byung yi ge nyid sprul pa'i gdung
NK034(ngi)001:92: ba bcad pa'i 'di nyid kyang rin chen lnga yi
NK034(ngi)001:93: rgyan dang bcas pa dang 'das rjes gsum po man
NK034(ngi)001:94: ngag snying gi nor su la snang ba de ni
NK034(ngi)001:95: mngon rdzogs 'gyur gang la snang bar gyur pa'i skal
NK034(ngi)001:96: ldan des rang gi zag bcas phung po ma zhig
NK034(ngi)001:97: bar rang nyid snying la bcangs te su la yang
NK034(ngi)001:98: bstan zhing bsgrags na rang srog 'tshig par 'gyur de
NK034(ngi)001:99: bas rang gi sems la rgyas thob cig gal te
NK034(ngi)001:100: phung po 'dor ba'i dus byung na skal ldan snying
NK034(ngi)001:101: gi bu la gtad par bya 'di yi gong du
NK034(ngi)001:102: gcig la bstan srid kyang dmyal khams me yis rang
NK034(ngi)001:103: gi lus sems bsreg de bas 'chi khar skal ldan
NK034(ngi)001:104: gcig la byin gnyis dang gsum las mang na chad
NK034(ngi)001:105: pa phog rin chen yi ge dag ni bris te
NK034(ngi)001:106: 'chang 'di ltar bgyis na byin rlabs chu rgyun ltar
NK034(ngi)001:107: rnal 'byor dam pa de la gnang ba'o gal te
NK034(ngi)001:108: bstan pa'i bdag po ma rnyed na phyi rabs don
NK034(ngi)001:109: du rin chen gter du sbos 'di ltar 'das rjes
NK034(ngi)001:110: gsum po'i don la reg gsang ba'i yang bcud snying
NK034(ngi)001:111: gi gdams pa'o gsang ba mchog de rdzogs pa yongs
NK034(ngi)001:112: rdzogs che de yi man ngag snying gi bcud phyungs
NK034(ngi)001:113: pa gzhan du bstan pa med pa'i snying thig ma
NK034(ngi)001:114: 'di yi mtshan tsam brjod par mi phod ste snying
NK034(ngi)001:115: gi yang bcud 'di nyid gsal bya'i phyir dbang bo'i
NK034(ngi)001:116: dwangs ma mig dang khong gi snying phyi ru phyungs
NK034(ngi)001:117: te skal ldan don ched du yi dam dam pa
NK034(ngi)001:118: 'di nyid 'bri bar bya gsang ba snying gi gzer
NK034(ngi)001:119: bu rig pa'i gnad lus dang ngag la brten nas
NK034(ngi)001:120: mngon sum du thob mthong 'phel ba'i rig pa 'di
NK034(ngi)001:121: dag nyid dbang po'i yul dang 'brel bar bstan pa'i
NK034(ngi)001:122: phyir snying tig yang bcud gsang ba kun gyi mchog
NK034(ngi)001:123: gsang ba'i yi ge ma ru snying gi nor sngon
NK034(ngi)001:124: chad phyungs pa med pa'i man ngag nyid theg pa
NK034(ngi)001:125: mtha' dag rnams dang mi 'dra ba'i snying gi dkyil
NK034(ngi)001:126: du mda' yis phog pa ltar phyir mi ldog par
NK034(ngi)001:127: byed pa'i thabs chen ni mtshan nas brjod par bla
NK034(ngi)001:128: ma brgyud pa dang mkha' 'gro rnams kyis bzod pa
NK034(ngi)001:129: chen po mdzod 'di dang 'phrad pa'i skal ldan nges
NK034(ngi)001:130: lung can zag bcas phung po 'byung ba rang zad
NK034(ngi)001:131: la 'gro bar 'gyur pa the tshom som nyi med
NK034(ngi)001:132: gal te snying po gsang ba'i don 'di dang 'phrad
NK034(ngi)001:133: ste nyams su ma blangs don g.yel na ma spyad
NK034(ngi)001:134: bzhag pa'i gter 'dra yon tan med de yi phyir
NK034(ngi)001:135: na snying po'i don 'di nyid nyams su long zhig
NK034(ngi)001:136: skal ldan snying gi bu snying po'i yang bcud gang
NK034(ngi)001:137: dang mi 'dra ba'i gsang chen nges pa'i snying po
NK034(ngi)001:138: 'di dag ni gzhan gyis thos par gyur na dngos
NK034(ngi)001:139: grub brlag mthong bas rnal 'byor rnams kyi 'bras bu
NK034(ngi)001:140: yal mtshan tsam nyid kyang brjod par bya ba min
NK034(ngi)001:141: 'byung ba'i dgras mi tshugs pa'i gnas nyid du brag
NK034(ngi)001:142: gi them pa nyid dam dben par ni lcags sam
NK034(ngi)001:143: zangs sam dngul gyi snod du bstsal rab tu sbas
NK034(ngi)001:144: te sus kyang mthong med par bzhugs su gsol te
NK034(ngi)001:145: skabs su lta ba'i tshe mkha' 'gro rnams la tshogs
NK034(ngi)001:146: gtor byin nas ni blta zhing spyad par bya ba
NK034(ngi)001:147: 'di nyid las gzhan du rang dgar spyod cing lta
NK034(ngi)001:148: ba min de yi phyir na thabs 'di mchog tu
NK034(ngi)001:149: gsang e ma 'di ltar ngo mtshar che ba yi
NK034(ngi)001:150: man ngag nges pa snying gi nor mchog 'di 'das
NK034(ngi)001:151: dang ma byon da ltar bzhugs pa yi sangs rgyas
NK034(ngi)001:152: rnams kyis 'di don gsungs pa dang gsung ba dang
NK034(ngi)001:153: ni gsung bar 'gyur ba min de yi phyir yang
NK034(ngi)001:154: thabs 'di mchog tu gsang rang gi rig pa mngon
NK034(ngi)001:155: sum ston pa yi yang gsang dril ba snying po
NK034(ngi)001:156: rnams kyi bcud 'di dang phrad pa'i skal ldan nges
NK034(ngi)001:157: lung can sangs rgyas nyid du 'gyur bar the tshom
NK034(ngi)001:158: med gal te nges pa'i snying po 'di nyid dang
NK034(ngi)001:159: phrad de don 'di nyams su ma blangs na bskal
NK034(ngi)001:160: pa bye ba brgya stong dung phyur du'ang sangs rgyas
NK034(ngi)001:161: 'bras bu nyid ni thob pa min de bas 'khrul
NK034(ngi)001:162: ba'i bya ba kun spangs te dur khrod dam ni
NK034(ngi)001:163: nags tshal chen po'i klong sus kyang rgyu ba med
NK034(ngi)001:164: pa'i gnas mchog nyid rab tu dben zhing dpag tshad
NK034(ngi)001:165: mang po yi grangs tshad 'das pa rnams kyi pha
NK034(ngi)001:166: rol tu lus dang ngag dang yid kyi gnad gcun
NK034(ngi)001:167: la su dang 'phrad pa med par gcig por 'dug
NK034(ngi)001:168: rang gi de nyid 'bral ba med par lta de
NK034(ngi)001:169: ltar gnas pas snying po'i don dang 'phrad yang dag
NK034(ngi)001:170: pa la snang ba 'di la 'gyur de ltar rab
NK034(ngi)001:171: tu gnas pa'i stobs med na lung stong ri rtse
NK034(ngi)001:172: la sogs nyid du yang rtag tu ngag bcad lkugs
NK034(ngi)001:173: pa lta bur rgyu gzhan gyis mthong na ri dwags
NK034(ngi)001:174: bzhin du 'bros 'di ltar byed pa'i skal ldan snying
NK034(ngi)001:175: gi bu yang dag dam tshig dam pa de la
NK034(ngi)001:176: yod rnal 'byor dbang phyug chen po zhes bya'o man
NK034(ngi)001:177: ngag snying po 'di ni nges pa'i thabs yang snying
NK034(ngi)001:178: dril ba su la bstan pa med des na gsang
NK034(ngi)001:179: chen dam pa mchog gi thabs rab tu gsang ste
NK034(ngi)001:180: rang gi yid la brnogs tshig zur tsam dang mtshan
NK034(ngi)001:181: yang brjod pa min mthong bar gyur na nges pa'i
NK034(ngi)001:182: 'bras bu yal sangs rgyas rnams kyi bde chen dam
NK034(ngi)001:183: pa'o shes rab kyis min dbang po'i yul can no
NK034(ngi)001:184: tshig gis 'di don rtogs pa ma yin te lce
NK034(ngi)001:185: yis brjod cing rna bar thos pa med brjod med
NK034(ngi)001:186: don de rnal 'byor dag gi gnas lag tu blang
NK034(ngi)001:187: ba'i man ngag tshig gsum mo 'di ltar yin no
NK034(ngi)001:188: sems kyi bu gcig po gzhan gyis 'di don gsal
NK034(ngi)001:189: bar ston pa med tshig gsum gyis ni sku gsum
NK034(ngi)001:190: snang ba ston 'di don gsang ba yin no s+aa
NK034(ngi)001:191: m+aa y+aa kha byang rnams su bkod pa med pa
NK034(ngi)001:192: yi rab tu gsang ba'i man ngag rnam bzhi nyid
NK034(ngi)001:193: kun la gsang ngo rang gi snying la phur gzhan
NK034(ngi)001:194: la brjod pa med do phyi rabs bu bdag gis
NK034(ngi)001:195: man ngag mang la longs spyad kyang man ngag 'di
NK034(ngi)001:196: don ston mi ma mthong ngo des na snying gi
NK034(ngi)001:197: snying mchog dam par zungs man ngag rnam pa bzhi
NK034(ngi)001:198: yi khong gi snying yi ge ma ru gsang ba
NK034(ngi)001:199: zangs yig can 'dra min gnyis las snying gi nor
NK034(ngi)001:200: mchog 'di khyad 'phags bstan pa kun gyi khong gzer
NK034(ngi)001:201: yin gsang ba snying gi man ngag bzhi med par
NK034(ngi)001:202: yi ge mang po dkar chab spungs pa 'dra don
NK034(ngi)001:203: med snying po'i don la reg pa med de kun
NK034(ngi)001:204: thad ka'i bden pa ston pa min snying thig gsang
NK034(ngi)001:205: ba zangs yig can med na lhag ma gsum yang
NK034(ngi)001:206: don med yugs sa rkyang des na legs par 'dril
NK034(ngi)001:207: ba 'di rang nyid rnal 'byor dam tshig rab dang
NK034(ngi)001:208: 'di phrad nas 'di don rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu 'grub
NK034(ngi)001:209: par shog +thii shes bya rang tshad phebs la phyag
NK034(ngi)001:210: 'tshal lo dngos po gshis kyi 'dug tshul gzhan gang
NK034(ngi)001:211: gis rtogs par 'gyur ba yang ni ma yin te
NK034(ngi)001:212: de don dbang po'i yul dang 'bral med par mthong
NK034(ngi)001:213: zhing dngos po rtsa ba lta bu ni gnad kyi
NK034(ngi)001:214: yi ge dam pa 'di bzhi la dum bu nges
NK034(ngi)001:215: pa'i grangs ni du yod pa ma bu nges pa
NK034(ngi)001:216: nyid ni 'di lta ste bstan pa thams cad 'dus
NK034(ngi)001:217: pa'i bu gcig po dum bu gcig ste ma bu
NK034(ngi)001:218: gnyis yod do sangs rgyas rnams kyi 'das rjes rnam
NK034(ngi)001:219: gsum la dum bu gsum ste ma bu gsum yod
NK034(ngi)001:220: do gsang ba rgyud kyi khog snying man ngag nyid
NK034(ngi)001:221: dung yig can la dum gcig ma bu bdun yang
NK034(ngi)001:222: gsang zab mo gsang ba snying thig ma yang gab
NK034(ngi)001:223: zangs kyi yi ge can la ni spros bcas rnams
NK034(ngi)001:224: la dum bu bcu drug yod spros med rnams la
NK034(ngi)001:225: dum bu gcig gis ston bu brgyad ma dang dgu
NK034(ngi)001:226: yis don gnyis 'grub de ltar rab zab man ngag
NK034(ngi)001:227: rnam bzhi la dum bu ma bu'i rtog pa bcad
NK034(ngi)001:228: pa'i phyir gsang ba'i kha byang dems zhes bya ba'o
NK034(ngi)001:229: +thii rang sems nges pa'i dpal la phyag 'tshal lo
NK034(ngi)001:230: rtsa rnams mdud pa rnam bzhi nyid dang ni skye
NK034(ngi)001:231: gnas nyid dang snying dang mgrin pa dang tshangs pa'i
NK034(ngi)001:232: bu ga dag la mdud pa ltar gsang chen rgyud
NK034(ngi)001:233: dang man ngag bsam yas kyang snying po don gyi
NK034(ngi)001:234: man ngag bzhi la 'dus de yi man ngag rtsis
NK034(ngi)001:235: su byas pa ni dum bu'i ming dang ma bu'i
NK034(ngi)001:236: ming nyid dang rim pa gsal bar phye ste 'di
NK034(ngi)001:237: ltar 'bri kun la bstan pa med pa'i man ngag
NK034(ngi)001:238: bzhi rnal 'byor kun gyi snying gi nor yin pas
NK034(ngi)001:239: rang gi sems la zhe dag'i yid kyis 'grogs de
NK034(ngi)001:240: dag rnams kyi ma dang bu yi mtshan tshig tu
NK034(ngi)001:241: brjod par ba dag gis mi phod kyang bla ma
NK034(ngi)001:242: nyid dang mkha' 'gro'i rigs nyid la bzod par gsol
NK034(ngi)001:243: te phyi rabs don nyid du dum bu nges pa'i
NK034(ngi)001:244: grangs 'di sems la brnogs 'das rjes rnam pa gsum
NK034(ngi)001:245: gyi dum bu ni dga' ldan gnas babs 'das rjes
NK034(ngi)001:246: dang po ni man ngag rnams kyi rtsa ba dang
NK034(ngi)001:247: por bstan gsang chen rol pa'i dur khrod nyid bababa
NK034(ngi)001:248: pa dang po nyid kyi 'grel pa'i tshul du bstan
NK034(ngi)001:249: gsum pa bya rgod phung po'i rir babs pa gnyis
NK034(ngi)001:250: pa dag gi t+ai ka'i tshul du bstan de ltar
NK034(ngi)001:251: dum bu gsum gyis 'das rjes rdzogs de bas mang
NK034(ngi)001:252: na snying po'i don nyid bslad nyung bar gyur na
NK034(ngi)001:253: man ngag kha mi skong de yi phyir na gsang
NK034(ngi)001:254: ba'i kha byang gces rang gi snying las lhag pa'i
NK034(ngi)001:255: zangs yig ma 'di yi mtshan tsam brjod par 'phangs
NK034(ngi)001:256: na yang de nyid dum bu nges pa 'di lta
NK034(ngi)001:257: ste gang zhig spros la dga' ba'i gang zag gis
NK034(ngi)001:258: dum bu'i ming des 'di dag nges par zungs spros
NK034(ngi)001:259: pa gcod pa'i sgron mas 'byung ba'i bslab thabs bstan
NK034(ngi)001:260: goms pa gnad kyi man ngag drug gis mtshon pa'i
NK034(ngi)001:261: gzhi ma bstan sems nyid sbyong bar byed pa thabs
NK034(ngi)001:262: kyi man ngag gis dman pa rnams kyi 'jug pa'i
NK034(ngi)001:263: rim pa bstan des na ris chad rjes su bzung
NK034(ngi)001:264: ba'i man ngag gces sbas pa mig 'byed kyis ni
NK034(ngi)001:265: lta sgom spyod pa bstan spyod pa bsdus pa'i sgron
NK034(ngi)001:266: mas spyod pa'i mtshan nyid bstan sgom pa bsdus pa'i
NK034(ngi)001:267: sgron mas mig gi sgom pa bstan lta ba bsdus
NK034(ngi)001:268: pa'i sgron mas phyi nang lta ba bstan 'bras bu
NK034(ngi)001:269: bsdus pa nyid kyis 'bras bu'i thob tshul bstan nyams
NK034(ngi)001:270: len bcud thag nyid kyis sngon 'gro'i man ngag bstan
NK034(ngi)001:271: bcos pa lus kyi gnad kyis rig pa yul la
NK034(ngi)001:272: bstan rgan mo mdzub tshugs kyis ni rig pa'i lta
NK034(ngi)001:273: lugs bstan rig pa sbar zin gyis ni rig pa'i
NK034(ngi)001:274: 'char lugs bstan rig pa'i rgyab brten bcud rnams bsdus
NK034(ngi)001:275: pa'i snying pos yid ches gtan la phab 'gal ba
NK034(ngi)001:276: bsdus pa'i sgron mas 'gal nyams gtan la phab gzhan
NK034(ngi)001:277: 'dod bsdus pa'i gcud phur gyis ni gzhan lta'i 'dod
NK034(ngi)001:278: pa dgag rig pa bsdus pa'i sgron mas rig pa
NK034(ngi)001:279: gtan la phab sku gsum bsdus pa'i sgron mas sku
NK034(ngi)001:280: gsum rang la sbyar lta sgom bsdus pa'i sgron mas
NK034(ngi)001:281: rnam gsum rig par sbyar nyag cig bsdus pa'i sgron
NK034(ngi)001:282: mas chos sku'i thig le nyag cig bstan dge sdig
NK034(ngi)001:283: bsdus pa'i sgron mas 'khor 'das la yang bzla de
NK034(ngi)001:284: ltar nyer gcig dum bus gsang ba zangs yig rdzogs
NK034(ngi)001:285: shes rab zab mo'i blo yis yang brtags na dum
NK034(ngi)001:286: bu bzhi bcu rtsa gcig dag tu nges spros med
NK034(ngi)001:287: rnams ni snying thig nyams len dngos 'di yis rnal
NK034(ngi)001:288: 'byor rnams kyi don chen 'grub de las mang na
NK034(ngi)001:289: gsang ba zangs yig 'chal nyung bar gyur na snying
NK034(ngi)001:290: po'i don mi rnyed de yi phyir na gsang ba'i
NK034(ngi)001:291: kha byang gces gsang ba'i man ngag dung yig can
NK034(ngi)001:292: nyid la shes rab zhib mo'i blo yis yang brtags
NK034(ngi)001:293: na dum bu bco brgyad rgyud kyi mtshan gyis shes
NK034(ngi)001:294: 'di las mang na gsang ba'i man ngag bslad nyung
NK034(ngi)001:295: bar gyur na don gyi snying po nyams de yi
NK034(ngi)001:296: phyir na gsang ba'i kha byang gces +thii rang gi
NK034(ngi)001:297: cha rkyen rdzogs la phyag 'tshal lo nges pa'i snying
NK034(ngi)001:298: po rang bzhin don gyi bcud rnam bzhi gzhan du
NK034(ngi)001:299: grags pa med pa'i chos snying thig srang la phab
NK034(ngi)001:300: pa 'di dag la gsal byed snying po bu yi
NK034(ngi)001:301: ming nyid ni nges pa tshig tsam brjod par mi
NK034(ngi)001:302: phod kyang bla ma yi dam rnams la gsol btab
NK034(ngi)001:303: nas gnad kyi man ngag 'di dag gsal bya'i phyir
NK034(ngi)001:304: skal ldan sems kyi bu yi don nyid du gsang
NK034(ngi)001:305: ba'i snying po 'di dag tshig tu bkod snying po
NK034(ngi)001:306: nges pa'i rang snang 'di lta bu ya mtshan mchog
NK034(ngi)001:307: tu che ba'i gsang ba nyid gnad kyi snying po
NK034(ngi)001:308: 'di kun yid la brnogs rdo rje 'chang gi tshig
NK034(ngi)001:309: gnad nges pa med na mchod pa'i dus mi shes
NK034(ngi)001:310: de ltar ma dang bu gnyis bsdebs pas bstan pa
NK034(ngi)001:311: bu gcig 'grub de yi phyir na gsang ba'i kha
NK034(ngi)001:312: byang gces gsang ba zangs yig med na gdams pa
NK034(ngi)001:313: gnad mi khrol rig 'dzin zhal chems med na 'jug
NK034(ngi)001:314: sgo gsal ba min de ltar bu gnyis ma dang
NK034(ngi)001:315: gsum gyis 'das rjes gsum pa 'grub de yi phyir
NK034(ngi)001:316: na gsang ba'i kha byang gces chags pa'i pra khrid
NK034(ngi)001:317: med na chags can lam mi tshud rlung gi pra
NK034(ngi)001:318: khrid med na nyams len dus mi shes yang gab
NK034(ngi)001:319: sbas dum med na zab pa'i gnad mi shes mdo
NK034(ngi)001:320: byang bsdus pa'i sgron ma med na dmigs pa'i ral
NK034(ngi)001:321: mi phyed dmigs gtad gsal ba'i sgron ma med na
NK034(ngi)001:322: lhag chad ngo mi shes gsang ba rtags yig med
NK034(ngi)001:323: na yid ches gdeng dang bral tshad kyi yi ge
NK034(ngi)001:324: med na dus kyi tshad mi zin gsang ba rgyab
NK034(ngi)001:325: yig med na don med yugs sa rkyang /
NK034(ngi)001:326: de ltar bu brgyad ma dang dgu yis gsang ba
NK034(ngi)001:327: zangs yig 'grub de yi phyir na gsang ba'i kha
NK034(ngi)001:328: byang gces pra khrid ma gtogs dung yig can yang
NK034(ngi)001:329: 'dra snying thig zab mo don gyii man ngag la
NK034(ngi)001:330: ma dang bu ste dum bu'i rtog pa can 'di
NK034(ngi)001:331: ltar don la yid ches gsal byas pas phyi rabs
NK034(ngi)001:332: 'jug pa'i skal ldan sems kyi bu the tshom yid
NK034(ngi)001:333: gnyis blo dang bral nas ni snying po'i don rnams
NK034(ngi)001:334: bde blag nyid du yang ma nor 'khrul pa med
NK034(ngi)001:335: pa'i sems kyis rtogs de yi phyir na gsang ba'i
NK034(ngi)001:336: kha byang 'di 'jug sgo gsal ba'i don du bdag
NK034(ngi)001:337: gis byas yang dag snying po bde ba chen po
NK034(ngi)001:338: ste rang snang chen po sgro 'dogs kun dang bral
NK034(ngi)001:339: kun gyis mthong ba med pa'i ye shes te sprul
NK034(ngi)001:340: sku bsgrub ste gzhan gyi don byed phyir 'byung ba
NK034(ngi)001:341: rnams kyi sgra la goms byed pa 'byung ba chen
NK034(ngi)001:342: po bcom ldan 'das 'gro ba kun la yang dag
NK034(ngi)001:343: gnas de nyid sngon 'gro'i spyod pa gsum lus sems
NK034(ngi)001:344: gnad la 'bebs pa ni thabs kyis gar thabs spyod
NK034(ngi)001:345: pa yis +aa li k+aa li rab tu bstan ji
NK034(ngi)001:346: ltar bsam pa bsam gtan nyid de rjes sor 'jug
NK034(ngi)001:347: cho ga ni mi g.yo ba ni sku yi rgya
NK034(ngi)001:348: mi brjod pa ni ye shes te mi len pa
NK034(ngi)001:349: ni bdag med cing des na lus ngag yid kyi
NK034(ngi)001:350: gnad de la bskyod pa med bzhin du rna dbang
NK034(ngi)001:351: gzhan la thos mi 'gyur de bzhin lce yi dbang
NK034(ngi)001:352: pos kyang brjod par bya ba rdul tsam med gcig
NK034(ngi)001:353: ste rnam pa yongs kyi med de nas rig pa'i
NK034(ngi)001:354: yul bstan pa rnal 'byor nam mkha'i bya lam gnas
NK034(ngi)001:355: de nas rig pa nyid bstan pa de la de
NK034(ngi)001:356: bstan de yang thob de nyid thabs kyi khyad par
NK034(ngi)001:357: ni zla ba las byung rten dang bcas rig pa
NK034(ngi)001:358: mngon par snang ba ni mngon sum bde ba rang
NK034(ngi)001:359: las 'byung de nyid rig pa'i ngo bo ni bzung
NK034(ngi)001:360: bas mi zin chu zla 'dra de nyid snang ba
NK034(ngi)001:361: gong 'phel bas de la phyogs kyi 'od 'dus pas
NK034(ngi)001:362: ngo mtshar rmad byung rol pa ni rig pa tshad
NK034(ngi)001:363: la phebs pa ste bya ba med pa'i las rnams
NK034(ngi)001:364: te chos rnams zad pa'i sar phyin pa zab gcig
NK034(ngi)001:365: na / zab pa'i cha shas sogs yul med zer /
NK034(ngi)001:366: mo'i cha zhes rtog yul med tha tshig ming du
NK034(ngi)001:367: btags pa med sgro btags chos kun ga la yod
NK034(ngi)001:368: de ltar lung chen rnams kyis mtshon nas ni rig
NK034(ngi)001:369: pa'i ye shes mngon sum gtan la phab rang bzhin
NK034(ngi)001:370: rdzogs pa chen po'i man ngag dang 'gal ba med
NK034(ngi)001:371: cig dbang po'i gnad dang bstun gzhan gyi man ngag
NK034(ngi)001:372: tshad phebs rgyab yig dang rang gi snang ba gtan
NK034(ngi)001:373: la dbab pa'i gzer nges par gtan la phab pa
NK034(ngi)001:374: 'di nyid do rnal 'byor rnams kyi gsang chen dam
NK034(ngi)001:375: pa'o sangs rgyas rnams kyi dgongs pa nyag cig dang
NK034(ngi)001:376: rig pa nyid kyi ye shes zang ka ma yul
NK034(ngi)001:377: la gcer mthong nyid du ston pa'i phyir sangs rgyas
NK034(ngi)001:378: sprul pa dga' rab rdo rje yis snying gi srang
NK034(ngi)001:379: la phab pa'i man ngag nyid yi ge ma ru
NK034(ngi)001:380: gsang ba snying thig ma gzhan du bstan re mkha'
NK034(ngi)001:381: 'gro rnam gsum dbang de yi phyir na gsang ba
NK034(ngi)001:382: man ngag snying rang sems stong pa nyid la rgyas
NK034(ngi)001:383: btab la skal ldan sems kyi bu dang ma 'phrad
NK034(ngi)001:384: par chu srin pir gyi gre ba bzhin du bsdam
NK034(ngi)001:385: gal te skal pa 'jig pa'i dus byung na rang
NK034(ngi)001:386: gi yid la rang gis rgyas btab la khong du
NK034(ngi)001:387: sbrul zhugs lus la me shor yang ji srid gnas
NK034(ngi)001:388: pa'i bar du khar mi dbyung de nas bstan pa
NK034(ngi)001:389: kun gyi btsas su sbos dngos grub 'dod pa'i rnal
NK034(ngi)001:390: 'byor dam pa yis skabs su mchod cing skabs su
NK034(ngi)001:391: bltas pa yis mchog dang thun mong gnyis la ci
NK034(ngi)001:392: dgar rol rig pa mngon sum lta ba'i me long
NK034(ngi)001:393: nyid zangs kyi yi ge rnal 'byor kun gyi snying
NK034(ngi)001:394: skal ldan sems kyi bu dang 'di phrad nas lus
NK034(ngi)001:395: ngag yid la bar chod mi 'byung bar rig pa'i
NK034(ngi)001:396: ye shes tshad la phebs par shog yang gsang dril
NK034(ngi)001:397: ba man ngag kun gyi snying sangs rgyas kun gyi
NK034(ngi)001:398: bde chen snying po'i don theg pa thun mong rnams
NK034(ngi)001:399: las khyad 'phags pa'i dbang po'i yul dang 'brel ba'i
NK034(ngi)001:400: gnad mchog 'di lus kyi gnad la brten nas mngon
NK034(ngi)001:401: sum par stong pa'i yul la 'gyur med srang du
NK034(ngi)001:402: tshud 'bral ba med cing rang gi don dam nyid
NK034(ngi)001:403: rtog pa ma yin mthong yul rnam par dag 'di
NK034(ngi)001:404: ltar ngag gi gnad la brten pas ni brjod du
NK034(ngi)001:405: med pa'i rang gnad yul la mthong de yi phyir
NK034(ngi)001:406: na gtan tshig lung gi gnad mi gsung mnyam par
NK034(ngi)001:407: bzhag pa sngags tshig yin sems kyi gnad la brten
NK034(ngi)001:408: pa yis me long nang du bzhin ltar bstan rig
NK034(ngi)001:409: pa'i ngo bo mngon du mthong de yi phyir na
NK034(ngi)001:410: nges pa'i bka' mngon sum pa dang rgyab nas 'byung
NK034(ngi)001:411: spyir na gsang sngags 'bras bu nyid mngon sum pa
NK034(ngi)001:412: dang phyi nas yin 'di ni rgyas thob ma yin
NK034(ngi)001:413: par mngon sum nyid du byed pas na 'bras bu
NK034(ngi)001:414: nyid las lam du byed gzhan gyi tshig gis ma
NK034(ngi)001:415: yin par rang gi mthu yis rig pa'o 'di dag
NK034(ngi)001:416: tshig tu bkod pa yis rig pa'i don la yid
NK034(ngi)001:417: ches pa mi 'gyur brtan pa'i don du'o rin chen
NK034(ngi)001:418: snying po lta ba'i 'debs snying du gdams te gsang
NK034(ngi)001:419: ba'i don phyi rabs skal ldan nges lung can 'jug
NK034(ngi)001:420: sgo gsal bar bya ba'i phyir yi ge dam pa
NK034(ngi)001:421: brjod pa'i sgo bla ma'i man ngag thugs kyi bcud
NK034(ngi)001:422: rgyal ba'i bka' dang 'gal med par sems kyi bu
NK034(ngi)001:423: yi don du bsdebs 'di la 'khrul pa yongs med
NK034(ngi)001:424: kyang gal te 'khrul pa byung srid na rgyal ba
NK034(ngi)001:425: sras dang bcas pa dang bla ma nyid dang mkha'
NK034(ngi)001:426: 'gro la bzod par gsol zhig sa ma y+aa de
NK034(ngi)001:427: yi phyir na 'khrul med dngos gsang ba'i gnad dang
NK034(ngi)001:428: bstun nas ni mtshan yang brjod par ma phod pa'i
NK034(ngi)001:429: snying thig gsang ba'i chos bzhi yi tshig la 'gyur
NK034(ngi)001:430: ba med pa'i phyir dbang po mig dang don gyi
NK034(ngi)001:431: snying lus kyi rtsa gnad ji bzhin du chos rnams
NK034(ngi)001:432: kun gyi gnad bkrol nas zab mo rnams kyi yang
NK034(ngi)001:433: zab pa snying po yang nas yang bsdus pa thig
NK034(ngi)001:434: le nyag cig mdor bsdus nas dgos don gsal ba
NK034(ngi)001:435: 'di nyid du bstan nas tshegs chung don che ba'i
NK034(ngi)001:436: snying po nyid la 'gyur med pa'i rin chen gsang
NK034(ngi)001:437: ba'i kha byang 'di skal ldan yid ches bskyed pa'i
NK034(ngi)001:438: phyir snying thig man ngag 'khrul med par nyams blang
NK034(ngi)001:439: tshad du phyin par shog gsang chen nges pa'i snying
NK034(ngi)001:440: po la rang dbang nyid du thob pa dang sku
NK034(ngi)001:441: gsum ye shes lnga rnams kyi snang ba lam du
NK034(ngi)001:442: rdzogs par shog mthar thug chen po'i tshad phebs dang
NK034(ngi)001:443: chos rnams zad pa'i sar skyol shog kha byang gi
NK034(ngi)001:444: rgyal po nyi mas brgyan pa zhes bya ba rab
NK034(ngi)001:445: tu zab pa rnams kyi man ngag mi 'gyur ba'i
NK034(ngi)001:446: don du mkhas pa chen po bi ma la mi
NK034(ngi)001:447: tras lho phyogs b+he ta'i yul rin po che snang
NK034(ngi)001:448: bar mdzad pa rdzogs so sa ma y+aa rgya rgya
NK034(ngi)001:449: rgya gu h+ya shu b+ham shog tshad nges pa'i kha
NK034(ngi)001:450: byang sgron ma rang gsal bzhugs tshad ldan rdo rje
NK034(ngi)001:451: 'dzin la phyag 'tshal lo rdo rje lta bu'i ye
NK034(ngi)001:452: shes chen po de gnyis med dbang po'i yul du
NK034(ngi)001:453: rtogs bya'i phyir rang snang bcar la 'bebs pa'i thabs
NK034(ngi)001:454: dag ni bla ma'i byin rlabs sngon gyi skal ba
NK034(ngi)001:455: dang rang gi dad pa mos gus byas pa la
NK034(ngi)001:456: brten nas gnyis med rang snang bde ba che dbang
NK034(ngi)001:457: po rnams kyi dwangs ma gang yin la brten nas
NK034(ngi)001:458: rdo rje lu gu rgyud de nyid mngon sum gsal
NK034(ngi)001:459: bar gtan la dbab pa'i phyir gzhan du bstan pa
NK034(ngi)001:460: med pa'i yi ge nyid rnam bzhi kha byang rnams
NK034(ngi)001:461: su ma bkod pa'i gsang chen snying dang 'dra ba'i
NK034(ngi)001:462: gdams pa la yi ge'i 'brel po shog bu'i grangs
NK034(ngi)001:463: nyid ni 'gyur ba med pa'i phyir na 'di dag
NK034(ngi)001:464: nyid bla ma'i gdams pa snying po'i rgyud rnams la
NK034(ngi)001:465: brten nas 'khrul pa med pa'i blo gros kyis rang
NK034(ngi)001:466: bzhin rdzogs chen rnams kyi bcud phyungs pa gsang ba'i
NK034(ngi)001:467: man ngag bzhi yi rgyan 'di bkod yang gsang dril
NK034(ngi)001:468: ba'i man ngag 'di dag la snying thig gsang ba
NK034(ngi)001:469: nges pa'i gnad dang bstun mngon sum nyid de rgyab
NK034(ngi)001:470: nas 'byung ba min snying po nges pa'i rang bzhin
NK034(ngi)001:471: 'di lta bu phyis kyang 'byung bar shin tu dkon
NK034(ngi)001:472: pa'o de yi don gyi tshad ni 'di lta bu
NK034(ngi)001:473: gzhan gyis bsgyur cing gzhig par dka' ba'i phyir shog
NK034(ngi)001:474: tshad snod kyi bye brag 'di lta ste rin chen
NK034(ngi)001:475: lnga yi rang byung byang bu ni sus kyang byas
NK034(ngi)001:476: shing bzo yis ma bsgrubs pa 'byung ba'i dgra dang
NK034(ngi)001:477: bral ba'i byang bu ni bzhi bcu brgyad de sus
NK034(ngi)001:478: kyang bshig tu med rang byung yi ge skad kyi
NK034(ngi)001:479: rigs ltar snang rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bgrang gis mi
NK034(ngi)001:480: langs pa'i byin brlabs nyid las rang snang nyid du
NK034(ngi)001:481: shar rin chen shel gyi glegs shing bar du gtems
NK034(ngi)001:482: rnam bdun rin chen gzer chen bzhi yis bsdams bstan
NK034(ngi)001:483: pa thams cad 'dus pa'i bu gcig po rang byung
NK034(ngi)001:484: yi ge 'byung ba'i sgra dang bral bcangs pa tsam
NK034(ngi)001:485: gyis bla med 'bras bu thob de phyir yi ge
NK034(ngi)001:486: 'di nyid gsang bar bya +thii rin chen mthing sngon
NK034(ngi)001:487: byang bu bcu drug la rin chen gser gyi yi
NK034(ngi)001:488: ges spras pa ste zangs kyi d+r+wa ba'i nang du
NK034(ngi)001:489: bcug pa ni 'das rjes gsum pa nyid de rab
NK034(ngi)001:490: tu gsang +thii ra gan glegs bu'i byang bu lnga
NK034(ngi)001:491: bcu la dkar po dung zhun yi ger btab pa
NK034(ngi)001:492: ni gsang ba dung yig can te 'di yang gsang
NK034(ngi)001:493: +thii ra gan glegs bu'i byang bu drug cu la
NK034(ngi)001:494: dmar po zangs zhun yi ger btab pa ni rin
NK034(ngi)001:495: chen mchong gi glegs shing bar du gtems rin chen
NK034(ngi)001:496: lnga yi gzer chen gnyis kyis bsdams bse yi sgrom
NK034(ngi)001:497: bu khong nag nang du bstsal gsang ba'i man ngag
NK034(ngi)001:498: zangs yig can de ni rab tu gsang bas rnam
NK034(ngi)001:499: 'byor don rab 'grub de yi phyir na yang gsang
NK034(ngi)001:500: dril ba'i bcud su la'ang mi bstan rang gi snying
NK034(ngi)001:501: la phur snying gi man ngag yi ge rnam pa
NK034(ngi)001:502: bzhi gzhan la ma ster rang gi sems la sbos
NK034(ngi)001:503: +thii de dag rnams kyi bu yi shog bu'i tshad
NK034(ngi)001:504: yi ge'i rgyu dang snod kyi bye brag ni rin
NK034(ngi)001:505: chen mthing shog byang bu bcu drug la ser po
NK034(ngi)001:506: gser gyi yi ge btab pa ni dar tshon lngas
NK034(ngi)001:507: gril gser gyi skud pas bcings rdo rje 'chang gsung
NK034(ngi)001:508: mchod 'os rang bzhin tshig 'di nyid kyis ni bstan
NK034(ngi)001:509: pa bu gcig gi man ngag yig sna lhag ma
NK034(ngi)001:510: med par rdzogs gzhan la gsang ste tshig tu mi
NK034(ngi)001:511: brjod do +thii pra khrid rnam pa gnyis la shog
NK034(ngi)001:512: dril chung ba gcig kha byang rnam pa gnyis la
NK034(ngi)001:513: shog dril chung ba gcig rtags kyi yi ge de
NK034(ngi)001:514: nyid la shin tu chung ba gcig gsang ba'i tshad
NK034(ngi)001:515: yig la yang shin tu chung ba gcig 'di dag
NK034(ngi)001:516: rin chen gser gyi skud pas sbrel nas ni mu
NK034(ngi)001:517: tig sngon po'i dra ba'i nang du bcug nas dril
NK034(ngi)001:518: gsang ba rgyab yig nyid la po ti chag gang
NK034(ngi)001:519: ba glegs shing phra mo gser gyi 'jim bag can
NK034(ngi)001:520: gyis gtems lcags kyi gzer chen sgo lcags kyis btab
NK034(ngi)001:521: ste za 'og gur khyim gser thig can gyis gril
NK034(ngi)001:522: 'di dag rnams kyis snying thig zangs yig gi man
NK034(ngi)001:523: ngag yig sna lhag chad med par rdzogs 'di dag
NK034(ngi)001:524: rang gi sems la brnags par bya skal med la
NK034(ngi)001:525: bstan mkha' 'gros snying khrag 'jibs de bas sems kyi
NK034(ngi)001:526: bu gcig ma gtogs pa tshig gi zur tsam gzhan
NK034(ngi)001:527: la bstan pa'am brjod cing bshad par mi bya sems
NK034(ngi)001:528: la phur gal te skal ldan sems kyi bu gcig
NK034(ngi)001:529: dang phrad de ster na dbang bzhi rdzogs byas la
NK034(ngi)001:530: 'di nyid bstan te nyams su blangs pa yis rdo
NK034(ngi)001:531: rje 'chang dang mnyam pa nyid du yang 'gyur ba
NK034(ngi)001:532: 'di la the tshom ci ste za dbang bzhi rdzogs
NK034(ngi)001:533: pa'i skal ldan snying gi bu sku gsum nyid dang
NK034(ngi)001:534: mnyam par 'di nyid la smos ci dgos te de
NK034(ngi)001:535: nyid rang yin no de yi phyir na 'di yang
NK034(ngi)001:536: rab tu gsang +thii kha byang gsum po gong dang
NK034(ngi)001:537: 'dra ba la tshad dang rtags yig gnyis la shog
NK034(ngi)001:538: dril chung ba gcig gsang ba rgyab yig la ni
NK034(ngi)001:539: po ti phyed de dag dung gi ba thag dkar
NK034(ngi)001:540: pos sbrel nas ni dung gi ga'u sbrul chen 'khyil
NK034(ngi)001:541: ba'i nang na yod de dag rnams kyis gsang ba
NK034(ngi)001:542: dung yig gi bu yig tshad rnams gtan la phab
NK034(ngi)001:543: pa yin 'di dag rnams kyi ma dang bu yig
NK034(ngi)001:544: ni kun la gsang ngo rang gi sems la brnags
NK034(ngi)001:545: byang khog dmar po'i nang du a tham mo gsang
NK034(ngi)001:546: chen man ngag dam pa 'di nyid ni skal ldan
NK034(ngi)001:547: sems kyi bu gcig ma gtogs par lung med sems
NK034(ngi)001:548: can don la mi mos la rlung dang ser bu'i
NK034(ngi)001:549: phyogs tsam nyid du yang bsgrag par bya ba min
NK034(ngi)001:550: no sems kyi bu rab tu gsang bas dngos grub
NK034(ngi)001:551: ci dgar rol de yi phyir na rang gi snying
NK034(ngi)001:552: la phur +thii gsang chen man ngag dam pa rnam
NK034(ngi)001:553: pa bzhi su la'ang bstan pa med pa snying gi
NK034(ngi)001:554: nor yang gsang bcud bsdus yi ge dkar dmar gnyis
NK034(ngi)001:555: mtshan tsam brjod par su'ang mi phod do 'brid mkhas
NK034(ngi)001:556: g.yon can kha gsag slu ba yis 'di nyid kha
NK034(ngi)001:557: drangs brid de ming tsam yang gal te mchan tshig
NK034(ngi)001:558: tsam du 'di shor na de la dgos pa'i don
NK034(ngi)001:559: du 'dra min gnyis ming mthun don du khyad par
NK034(ngi)001:560: che bar bstan gsang ba snying gi snying thig 'di
NK034(ngi)001:561: dag nyid kha byang rnams kyi nang du bkod pa
NK034(ngi)001:562: med de yi phyir na gsang ba'i kha byang 'di
NK034(ngi)001:563: sus kyang mthong du rung ba ma yin no de
NK034(ngi)001:564: yi phyir na snying 'dra'i gdams pa 'di nags klong
NK034(ngi)001:565: nyid dam dur khrod mi med sar grogs med gcig
NK034(ngi)001:566: pur 'dug ste 'di nyid la nyams su blangs te
NK034(ngi)001:567: grub pa'i 'bras bu gdon gsang ba 'di ni bde
NK034(ngi)001:568: chen gsang ba'i gnas gzhan du med de 'di nyid
NK034(ngi)001:569: bcud phyungs nas sangs rgyas rnams kyis gshegs pa'i shul
NK034(ngi)001:570: de nyid 'di nyid rang du tshad la phab nas
NK034(ngi)001:571: ni bla ma'i zhal la lus pa med par yang
NK034(ngi)001:572: tshig don gsal bar yi ge nyid du bkod rang
NK034(ngi)001:573: rig rgyu rkyen gnyis la ma ltos pas shes rab
NK034(ngi)001:574: kyis ni spyod yul min pa'i phyir dbang po nyid
NK034(ngi)001:575: la rno dang rtul med par 'di nyid mthong ste
NK034(ngi)001:576: don rig nyams blangs na gsang sngags rnams kyi 'bras
NK034(ngi)001:577: bu 'di nyid la thob par 'gyur ba 'di la
NK034(ngi)001:578: the tshom med de yi phyir na gsang ba nges
NK034(ngi)001:579: pa'i gnad bshad cing bstan pa mi dgos ngo mtshar
NK034(ngi)001:580: che yang dag ye shes tshig gis mi rtogs te
NK034(ngi)001:581: mngon sum rang gnad tshad 'di ngo mtshar che rang
NK034(ngi)001:582: bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i don de nyid dge sdig
NK034(ngi)001:583: gnyis kyis phan gnod la bzlas phyir dbang po nyid
NK034(ngi)001:584: dang 'brel ba ngo mtshar che smra bsam brjod du
NK034(ngi)001:585: med pa'i don de nyid gzhan gyis bshad pas de
NK034(ngi)001:586: don mi rnyed phyir rang gi gnad las byung ba
NK034(ngi)001:587: ngo mtshar che gsang ba chen po sus kyang ma
NK034(ngi)001:588: rnyed pa theg pa thun mong rnam las khyad 'phags
NK034(ngi)001:589: phyir nges pa'i don nyid gsung pa ngo mtshar che
NK034(ngi)001:590: bla ma'i man ngag rkyen la rag ma lus rang
NK034(ngi)001:591: snang dbang po'i gnad dang bstun nas ni sngon chad
NK034(ngi)001:592: mthong ma myong ba'i yul de nyid goms shing sbyangs
NK034(ngi)001:593: pa mi dgos cig car du stong pa'i yul la
NK034(ngi)001:594: lhag mthong nyid du yong las la dag dang ma
NK034(ngi)001:595: dag med pa'i mis mngon sum nyid du mthong bar
NK034(ngi)001:596: gyur ba la the tshom yod pa nyid ni ma
NK034(ngi)001:597: yin no de yi phyir na gsang ba'i thabs chen
NK034(ngi)001:598: 'di sangs rgyas thugs rje ldan pa rnams kyis kyang
NK034(ngi)001:599: snying thig 'di ni brjod par nus ma yin de
NK034(ngi)001:600: yi phyir na sangs rgyas thams cad kyis rdo rje
NK034(ngi)001:601: 'chang la dbang bzhi rdzogs byas nas gsang ba mchog
NK034(ngi)001:602: la dbang bar dbang bskur bas nyid kyi gsang don
NK034(ngi)001:603: 'di ni brjod pa las gzhan gyis gsung zhing bstan
NK034(ngi)001:604: par nus mi srid de yi phyir na thabs chen
NK034(ngi)001:605: snying bcud 'di rab tu gsang bar bya'o sa ma
NK034(ngi)001:606: y+aa shog bu'i tshad dang yi ge'i rgyu nyid dang
NK034(ngi)001:607: snod dang bcas pa gsang ba'i yi ger bkod 'di
NK034(ngi)001:608: yi dge bas don dam de nyid la dbang thob
NK034(ngi)001:609: sku gsum lam du snang bar shog shog tshad gsal
NK034(ngi)001:610: ba'i kha byang sgron ma rang gsal zhes bya ba
NK034(ngi)001:611: mkhas pa chen po bi ma la mi tras mdzad
NK034(ngi)001:612: pa rdzogs so dpal sngags srung gi rgyal mo e
NK034(ngi)001:613: ka tsa tis srungs shig sa ma y+aa pa tram
NK034(ngi)001:614: traka1&&& a tham gter nas gter du dam par btsas
NK034(ngi)001:615: nas bka' gzhan du ma 'khyar ba lags so yi
NK034(ngi)001:616: ge dkar dmar gnyis la 'dra min zhes kyang bya
NK034(ngi)001:617: mi 'dra ba'i yi ge gnyis bzhugs pa la snying
NK034(ngi)001:618: thig gi kha byang 'dir bkod pa'i ma bu rnams
NK034(ngi)001:619: snying thig lags so mi 'dra mi zab pa de
